<description>&lt;div class="pageBefore">&lt;img src="http://78.46.73.113/wiki/images/z.gif" width="1" height="1" border="0" alt="" style="display:block" align="top" />&lt;/div>&lt;div class="page">
&lt;b>Сравнение версий &lt;a  href="http://78.46.73.113/wiki/wakka.php?wakka=DokumentacijaIPStudioAMBS/RoamingServices&amp;amp;v=1dil" class="">/Документация&amp;nbsp;IP&amp;nbsp;Studio&amp;nbsp;AMBS&amp;nbsp;/&amp;nbsp;Roaming&amp;nbsp;Services&lt;/a> за &lt;a href="http://78.46.73.113/wiki/wakka.php?wakka=DokumentacijaIPStudioAMBS/RoamingServices&amp;amp;time=2007-08-30+15%3A31%3A17">2007-08-30 15:31:17&lt;/a> и &lt;a href="http://78.46.73.113/wiki/wakka.php?wakka=DokumentacijaIPStudioAMBS/RoamingServices&amp;amp;time=2007-08-30+17%3A01%3A52">2007-08-30 17:01:52&lt;/a>&lt;/b>&lt;br />
